overview.en: ORA sharing and transparency is the core concept of block chain. It will integrate the pain points in the agricultural and sideline products industry to achieve landing application. The premise of combining agricultural and sideline products is to create a perfect ecological supply plan and integrate block chain technology into projects.
overview.zh: ORA共享和透明是区块链的核心理念，真实将目前农副产品行业的痛点进行整合，实现落地应用。结合农副产品的前提是打造完美的生态供给方案，将区块链技术融合于项目中。
